### Duplicate — identical to Ahmad above. Job logs "Duplicate lead ignored", no new row.
POST {{host}}/api/leads
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Ahmad bin Ismail",
  "email": "ahmad.ismail@example.com",
