}

### Invalid input — expect 422 JSON (bad email, negative bill, unknown enum + state)
POST {{host}}/api/leads
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Bad Lead",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "phone": "",
  "monthly_bill_rm": -5,
  "property_type": "villa",
  "roof_type": "tile",
  "state": "Penang"
}
